data.title: CASEY DESMOND w/ Maria Demaio, Sam James
data.text:
At nineteen years old, Casey Desmond has already recorded three albums, written and recorded with Grammy Winning artists like Will Ackerman, and received airplay on AAA and college radio across the US and Canada. Her music has the rock sensibility of Sheryl Crow, pop/harmonies of Liz Phair, and the attitude of Chrissy Hynde. See her with talented singer/songwriters Maria Demaio and Sam James.

Get your tickets now at www.cwconcerts.com
